WEBVTT

00:02:59.585 --> 00:03:01.746
na wakati wa kuraribika ikiwadia
wanatofua

00:03:02.130 --> 00:03:04.455
Wakati mwingine, hutoka vituo vya afya

00:03:04.479 --> 00:03:07.555
kama hospitali, famasia,na
uguzia

00:03:07.579 --> 00:03:11.388
wanaobaki na ziada,
zisizomezwa

00:03:11.412 --> 00:03:13.212
au wakati wagonjwa wanapofariki.

00:03:13.236 --> 00:03:17.307
Tweza nufuika na haya
madawa ziada

00:03:17.331 --> 00:03:22.449
kusambazia watu milioni kumi
wanaohitaji haya madawa.

00:03:22.473 --> 00:03:24.117
Na tunaweza fanya hivyo leo.

00:03:24.589 --> 00:03:27.404
SIRUM inapata madawa ziada

00:03:27.428 --> 00:03:31.134
kwa kuweka chombo cha matumizi tena
kwa haya majumba